Invocation Name: my cafe
des:
Run a cafe through a series of difficult questions!

Each day, Alexa will ask you a difficult question. Depending on your answer, your cafe will thrive or take a hit.

Are you wise enough to beat your competitors? Do you have the business knowledge to keep your cafe alive among chaos? Make good decisions to keep your cafe alive as long as you can!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
